            What is game theory?
          </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image
          border-radius="10px"
          padding="10px 12px"
          width="600px"
          src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/putin-nato-game-theory.jpg"
          alt="Vladimir Putin sits with a contemplative expression behind a chessboard, with the NATO flag in the background, symbolizing strategic tensions between Russia and NATO."
